<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>- Fixed a bug that was allowing focused and Alternate Advancement ability enhanced damage spells to do more damage than they should (meaning that both the Alternate Advancement and the Focus improve the base damage. The focus damage was never supposed to compound with the added AA damage.)<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
